summary_bm: Kluster ini merupakan kluster berulang kali kedua melibatkan kakitangan sebuah pusat perkhidmatan yang terletak di Jalan Bank, Kuantan. Kes indeks bagi kluster ini merupakan Kes No. 2466062, perempuan, Warganegara Malaysia, berumur 28 tahun yang dilaporkan positif COVID-19 pada 30 Oktober 2021 hasil saringan individu bergejala. Kes mula bergejala pada 27 Oktober 2021.
summary_en: This cluster is the second recurring cluster involving staff of a service centre located at Jalan Bank, Kuantan. The index case for this cluster is Case No. 2466062, a female Malaysian citizen aged 28 years who reported positive COVID-19 on 30th October 2021 due to symptomatic individual screening. The case experienced symptoms starting on 27th October 2021.

summary_bm: Kluster ini melibatkan pelajar-pelajar di sebuah pusat pendidikan yang terletak di Kampung Cheroh, Raub. Kes mula bergejala pada 25 Oktober 2021.
summary_en: This cluster involves students at an educational centre located in Kampung Cheroh, Raub. The index case for this cluster is Case No. 2454043, a Malaysian citizen girl aged six years who reported positive for COVID-19 on 28th October 2021 due to symptomatic individual screening. The case experienced symptoms starting on 25th October 2021.

summary_bm: Kluster ini melibatkan penghuni-penghuni dan kakitangan sebuah pusat jagaan yang terletak di Kampung Dusun Raja, Panji, Kota Bharu. summary_en: This cluster involves the residents and staff of a care centre located in Kampung Dusun Raja, Panji, Kota Bharu. summary_en: This cluster involves staff and students at four (4) educational centers located at Jalan Tras, Raub.
